metadata.name: Infinity Sketch
metadata.description:
Sketching forms the foundation of all my work. Each painting, mural, collage and sculpture starts behind the pad with a pencil. 

To celebrate a 20 year evolution of dedication and style, I created this sketch for my limited edition sketchbook that was released in 2017. 

Sketching feels like an endless loop that brings me in a hyperfocus state where I can be free to push my visual boundaries as an artist. Iâ€™m never not sketching.
